### Store memory
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/memory/store
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Deployment preference: run dry-run validation before production rollout.",
  "namespace": "agent-session-1",
  "tags": ["deployment", "preference"],
  "reasoningChainId": "chain-42",
  "pinTtlMillis": 60000
}

### Recall memory
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/memory/recall
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Which validation should happen before production rollout?",
  "namespace": "agent-session-1",
  "topK": 5,
  "tokenBudget": 1024,
  "tags": ["deployment"],
  "scenario": "coding"
}

### Submit feedback
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/memory/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recallSessionId": "<recall-session-id>",
  "usedFragmentIds": ["<fragment-id>"],
  "answerAccepted": true
}

### Memory health
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/memory/health

